coconut oil contract to chang - dutch trader contract term for trade in coconut oil are to be chang from long ton to tonn with effect from the aug/sep contract onward , dutch veget oil trader said . oper have alreadi start to take account of the expect chang and report at least one trade in tonn for aug/sept shipment yesterday . the feder of oil seed and fat associ , fosfa , in london said it had previous advis trader to adopt the metric system for coconut oil transact to bring the commod into line with other veget oil .